definitions.definition: The capital city of Aichi Prefecture , in central Honshu , Japan .
Synonym of Lubuk Baja : a district of Batam , Riau Islands , Indonesia .

main_definition: The capital city of Aichi Prefecture , in central Honshu , Japan .
secondary_definitions: ( colloquial ) Synonym of Lubuk Baja : a district of Batam , Riau Islands , Indonesia .
